data.description: The perfect blend of comfort and style awaits in this Northwest Reno home!  Boasting 1270 sq ft of cozy interior, this charming single-story residence features a 3-bed, 2-bath layout with an attached 2-car garage. A covered front porch welcomes you to the property and provides space to sit and relax while enjoying the neighborhood scenery. Step inside to find an inviting great room with an abundance of natural light streaming through oversized windows, highlighting the wood-look laminate flooring and tall ceilings. A sliding glass door seamlessly connects the indoor and outdoor spaces. Enjoy the fully fenced rear yard, complete with a covered back porch, paver patio, and a large dog run, providing a fantastic space for entertaining. The thoughtfully updated kitchen is perfect for the at-home chef, offering recessed lighting, white cabinetry, a built-in dishwasher, microwave, gas range, and a convenient breakfast bar for additional seating capacity. Retreat to the light and bright primary bedroom featuring a ceiling fan and an ensuite bathroom with an oversized shower stall, creating a private space to rest at the end of a long day. Situated on a corner lot within a cul-de-sac, this property offers both convenience and plenty of privacy. Benefit from the freedom of no HOA and relish the proximity to several popular parks, schools, and shopping centers. Don't miss the opportunity to make this Northwest Reno gem your new home – schedule your showing today!
